      <title>委内瑞拉1540亿美元债务违约，准备对话</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/in-default-on-154-billion-of-debt-venezuela-is-ready-to-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过多年的断断续续，委内瑞拉正在为数十年来规模最大、最复杂的债务重组之一做好准备——解除从华尔街到俄罗斯债权人的 1540 亿美元违约债券、贷款和法律判决网。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/in-default-on-154-billion-of-debt-venezuela-is-ready-to-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 13:34:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
