      <title>农作物交易商重申前景疲弱，邦吉股价暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/bunge-profit-tops-estimates-as-crop-trader-weathers-downturn</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管第一季度盈利超出预期，但农业综合企业巨头邦吉全球公司 (Bunge Global SA) 重申利润前景疲弱，股价暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/bunge-profit-tops-estimates-as-crop-trader-weathers-downturn</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 10:20:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
