      <title>渣打银行的客户渴望石油和铜，被告知要谨防通货膨胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/stanchart-tells-clients-craving-oil-copper-to-beware-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行的一些客户越来越青睐铜和石油等有形资产，考虑到美国利率可能会走高，这种做法令该英国银行的首席策略师感到担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/stanchart-tells-clients-craving-oil-copper-to-beware-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:46:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
